Package prelim

Class DoublyCircularNode<T>

java.lang.Object
prelim.DoublyCircularNode<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of data stored in the node
public class DoublyCircularNode<T> extends Object
Represents a node in a doubly circular linked list. Each node contains a data element, and references to both the next and previous nodes in the circular list.
